message.body: Sorry, my love. Already at work. Hope you had fun tonight!
I did. It was really nice :) I'm sorry I missed you though! I love you!
Good good :) Love you too, and see you in a few days!
Good morning, beautiful! Before i pass out, i just want to tell you that i love you so so very very much. I cant tell you how badly i want tuesday to come :)
I can't wait to see you!!!!!
